snippet.textDisplay: I am a veterinary technician. Compassion fatigue is real and sometimes crushes me, but when I sit down to watch your videos with your dogs, it makes me feel so happy. You and Julien are a breath of fresh air and remind me why I got into veterinary medicine in the first place: to keep pets healthy so they and their animal-loving parents can be together as long as possible.
